"https://www.cnblogs.com/147api/p/archive/2026/02\"},{\"title\":\"Claude Opus 4.6 正式发布：Agent 时代的编程王者与长上下文革命\",\"url\":\"https://juejin.cn/post/7606640585463169051\"},{\"title\":\"Microsoft 开发人员更改日志\",\"url\":\"https://developer.microsoft.com/zh-cn/changelog\"},{\"title\":\"2026 最新教程：在国内怎么稳定使用 Claude Opus 4.6？（含 API 接入方法）\",\"url\":\"https://m.blog.csdn.net/weixin_41993692/article/details/157945161\"},{\"title\":\"2025年底到2026年初，GitHub Copilot依然是程序员最常用的AI编程助手，虽收费提高但凭借深度开发整合和智能辅助依旧受欢迎\",\"url\":\"https://baijiahao.baidu.com/s?id=1856952824055553014\"},{\"title\":\"快速入门：使用适用于 .NET 的 GitHub Copilot 应用现代化评估并迁移 .NET 项目\",\"url\":\"https://learn.microsoft.com/zh-cn/dotnet/azure/migration/appmod/quickstart?toc=/dotnet/navigate/migration-guide/toc.json\"},{\"title\":\"Claude Opus 4.6最强编程王上线，附国内5种使用方法\",\"url\":\"https://m.blog.csdn.net/qq_59308920/article/details/157805662\"}]\n\nLinks: [{\"title\":\"Claude Sonnet 4.6空降！Office性能干翻旗舰模型，软件股哀嚎一片\",\"url\":\"http://c.m.163.com/news/a/KM1V447S051180F7.html\"},{\"title\":\"Claude Sonnet 4.6 发布了，Anthropic 迄今最强的 Sonnet 模型。\",\"url\":\"https://3g.sina.com.cn/news/detail/5267532516688043.html\"},{\"title\":\"GitHub Copilot集成 GPT‑5.3‑Codex 代理式开发任务提速25%\",\"url\":\"https://www.toutiao.com/article/7605107886544667171/\"},{\"title\":\"负责任地使用 GitHub Copilot 代码评审\",\"url\":\"https://docs.github.com/zh/copilot/responsible-use-of-github-copilot-features/responsible-use-of-github-copilot-code-review\"},{\"title\":\"程序员的最后一块拼图：为什么你必须学会用Claude Code？\",\"url\":\"https://www.53ai.com/news/LargeLanguageModel/2026020775194.html\"},{\"title\":\"Claude Opus 4.6 模型新特性（2026年2月5日发布）\",\"url\":\"https://juejin.cn/post/7603616672927399951\"},{\"title\":\"对外卖Copilot，对内用Claude？微软内部正在悄悄换“编程大脑”(对外卖员的赞美句子)\",\"url\":\"https://m.jrhz.info/tech/2175432.html\"},{\"title\":\"Introducing Claude Code Playground Plugin for Interactive ...\",\"url\":\"https://www.linkedin.com/posts/shaimishali_anthropics-claude-code-has-a-new-plugin-activity-7423276775352467456-XP08\"},{\"title\":\"Claude Sonnet 4.6空降！Office性能干翻旗舰模型，软件股哀嚎一片\",\"url\":\"https://news.sina.cn/ai/2026-02-18/detail-inhnfayk1110055.d.html?fromsinago=nxbfercx\"},{\"title\":\"刚刚，Claude Opus 4.6 接入 VSCode！我全程没登录\",\"url\":\"https://new.qq.com/rain/a/20260207A07CXH00\"}]\n\nNo links found.\n\nLinks: [{\"title\":\"刚刚，Claude Sonnet 4.6 上线！我接入了 Clawdbot\",\"url\":\"https://new.qq.com/rain/a/20260218A04LGX00\"},{\"title\":\"Claude最新Sonnet：Opus级智能，性价比王炸，OpenClaw天选API\",\"url\":\"https://m.toutiao.com/article/7608119945771090467/\"},{\"title\":\"Claude最新Sonnet：Opus级智能，性价比王炸，OpenClaw天选API\",\"url\":\"https://baijiahao.baidu.com/s?id=1857450498655480638\"},{\"title\":\"Claude最新Sonnet: Opus级智能, 性价比王炸, OpenClaw天选API\",\"url\":\"https://mparticle.uc.cn/article_org.html?uc_param_str=frdnsnpfvecpntnwprdssskt#!wm_cid=736857996222540800!!wm_id=be5d4615193f4baa88756085e30589a3\"},{\"title\":\"Claude最新Sonnet：Opus级智能，性价比王炸，OpenClaw天选API\",\"url\":\"https://m.sohu.com/a/988296731_121207965/?pvid=000115_3w_a\"},{\"title\":\"急报！Claude Sonnet 4.6 发布！\",\"url\":\"http://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1naZ1B3EpQ\"},{\"title\":\"Claude Sonnet 4.6 发布\",\"url\":\"https://new.qq.com/rain/a/20260218A02IJ800\"},{\"title\":\"更 关键 的 是 sonnet 4 6 的 模型 标识 符 是 claude sonnet 4...\",\"url\":\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/Qsma6FMEe\"},{\"title\":\"Claude Opus 4.6 模型新特性（2026年2月5日发布）\",\"url\":\"https://juejin.cn/post/7603616672927399951\"},{\"title\":\"Claude Code 的完美平替：OpenCode + GitHub Copilot（顶级模型+最优价格）\",\"url\":\"https://post.m.smzdm.com/p/apw0e0pw/\"}]\n\nBased on my search, I was unable to find specific discussions from Reddit about the GitHub Copilot and Claude Sonnet 4.6 integration from February 2026. However, I found several relevant sources discussing the integration and user feedback from other platforms. Here's what I found:\n\n## GitHub Copilot + Claude 4.6 Integration Overview\n\n### Official Integration Status\nAccording to Microsoft's developer changelog and GitHub blog posts, **Claude Opus 4.6** became generally available in GitHub Copilot in **February 2026** for Copilot Enterprise, Business, Pro, and Pro+ subscribers. The model is accessible in GitHub Copilot Chat on github.com, VS Code (chat, ask, edit, agent modes), Visual Studio, GitHub Mobile, and CLI.\n\n### Claude Sonnet 4.6 Release (February 18, 2026)\nClaude Sonnet 4.6 was released on February 18, 2026, and GitHub Copilot has integrated this latest model as well.\n\n## User Feedback & Reviews Summary\n\n### Positive Feedback\n\n1. **Performance Improvements**\n   - In internal Anthropic testing, users preferred **Sonnet 4.6 over Sonnet 4.5 in 70% of cases**\n   - More impressively, **59% of users preferred Sonnet 4.6 over Opus 4.5** (the previous flagship model)\n   - Users reported better instruction following, fewer instances of \"laziness\" or over-engineering, and more stable multi-step task execution\n\n2. **Code Quality**\n   - Users noted Sonnet 4.6 **reads context more carefully before making code changes**\n   - It **merges duplicate logic** rather than copying and pasting code\n   - Hallucinations reduced by approximately 70%\n   - False success claims significantly decreased\n\n3. **Long Context Window**\n   - Sonnet 4.6 supports **1 million token context window** (beta)\n   - Users reported this is critical for handling large codebases without losing context\n\n4. **Frontend & Visual Capabilities**\n   - Multiple users reported improved frontend code generation\n   - Visual outputs described as more refined with better layout, animations, and design sense\n\n### Concerns & Criticisms\n\n1. **Security Concerns**\n   - Some developers expressed concern about **Agent mode security** in Copilot\n   - Worries about agents with production commit permissions posing supply chain risks if workflows are compromised\n\n2. **Opus 4.6 Performance**\n   - Some users felt Opus 4.6 didn't meet expectations compared to Sonnet 4.6\n   - Opus 4.6 recommended mainly for backend, question answering, and tool calling, while Sonnet 4.6 preferred for coding\n\n### GitHub Copilot Multi-Model Strategy\n- GitHub's strategy of integrating multiple AI models (Claude, GPT-5.3-Codex, Gemini) allows developers to choose different models for different tasks\n- This is seen as a response to competition from Cursor (which popularized Claude integration)\n\n---\n\n**Note**: I couldn't locate specific Reddit discussions (r/programming, r/github, etc.) about this topic, likely because:\n1. The content may be newer or less indexed\n2. Discussions might be happening in private communities or other forums\n3. The specific combination of search terms didn't match Reddit post titles\n\nFor the most current Reddit discussions, you may want to search directly on reddit.com for terms like \"Claude 4.6\", \"Sonnet 4.6 Copilot\", or check relevant subreddits manually.\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."
