able\n- Some users felt it left competitors like Cursor and Copilot \"far behind\"\n- The popularity was so significant that it allegedly caused concerns in the software stock market\n\n---\n\n**Sources:** The search results include articles from various Chinese tech platforms (163.com, Sina, Aliyun Developer, 36Kr) and GitHub discussions from January-February 2026, all discussing this major release."
